quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  2,220,"Ko jaЕӢtaa koo shar'iniraama ngam miijito-Й—on e ko nafata on aduna e laakara.WondiiЙ“e maa Й“en no naamno-maa, an Annabiijo, fii toppitagol yatiimatu (wonduЙ—o), hol no Й“e gerdata? HiЙ“e gasa jillindirde jawle maЙ“Й“e Й—en ka nafaqqa, e koltu e wondiigu? Jaabo Й“e maakaa: "Ko moЖҙЖҙoragol e maЙ“Й“e anngal jillondiral e jawle maЙ“Й“e Й—en Й“uri mawnude mbarjaari ka Allah, ko Й—um kadi moЖҙЖҙani jawle maЙ“Й“e Й—en; sabu Й—um reenay Й—e. Si on kafidii e maЙ“Й“e non jawle e wondiigu ekn, huunde fawaaki on, tawde ko Й“e musiЙ—Й“e mo'on ka diina; musiЙ—Й“e non, ko mballondira. Alla no Anndi on Й“en bonnooЙ“e e moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e immorde e Й“en toppitotooЙ“e wonduЙ“e. Si Mo Muuyunoo Й“iЙ—tinanngol on e Й“en yatimeeЙ“e, O WaЙ—ayno. Si ko woni, KaЕӢko SeniiЙ—o TedduЙ—o On, O Hoynanii on wondigal mon e maЙ“Й“e; sa
bu Diina Makko ko e Й—um mahii. Alla Ko FooluЙ—o Mo fooletaake, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o e Tageefo Makko ngon."
  2,221,"Wata on resu, onon muumini en, Й“en rewЙ“e shirkooЙ“e haa Й“e gomЙ—ina Alla, Й“e naata e diina lislaamu. Pellete ko ko korЙ—o gomЙ—inЙ—o Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude debbo dimo rewoowo (lawru; towru); hay si ЕӢari e jawle makko haawnii on. Wata on resin rewЙ“e juulЙ“e Й“en worЙ“e shirkooЙ“e. Pellet ko maccuЙ—o gomЙ—iЙ—o Alla e NulaaЙ—o Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude dimo shirkoowo, hay si o haawnii on. ЖҒen shirkooЙ“e (worЙ“e e rewЙ“e), hino noddira konngol e kuugal faade e yiite. Alla No Noddira e golle moЖҙЖҙe naadayЙ—e aljaana, newinira ya'fuyee Makko On e DuЕӢayee Makko. Himo Й“aЕӢnginana yimЙ“e Й“en Aayeeje Makko Й—en, belajo'o Й“e taskitoo e majje Й“e gollata Й—e."
  2,222,"WondiiЙ“e maa Й“en no naamno-maa, an Annabiijo, fii fiilordu, Й—am ЖҙiiЖҙam njaltoojam e rannga debbo e sahaaji keeriiЙ—i. Jaabo Й“e maakaa: Fiilordu, no nefinanii gorko e debbo. WoЙ—Й—itee renndugol e rewЙ“e Й“en fewndo mun, wata on Й“adorЙ“e renndiigu haa ЖҙiiЖҙam Й—am taЖҙa, Й“e laЙ“Й“iЕӢtinora lootngal. Si Й“e laaЙ“iЕӢtinorii lootngal ngal, renndiree e maЙ“Й“e no Alla Daginiri non: laaЙ“uЙ“e rannga. Alla No YiЙ—i Й“en hebbinorooЙ“e tuubugol e geddi, e Й“en faЕӢtinooЙ“e e laЙ“Й“inagl."
  2,223,"RewЙ“e mon Й“en ko sugu ngesa (joombuure) mon mban; hiЙ“e jibinana on Й“iЙ—Й“e wano ngesa jonnirta dimЙ—e. Ngardee ngesa mon mban (farji on) nokku ka ka njiЙ—Й—on e no njiЙ—irЙ—on, fotde ko ka farji. ngardinanee ko'e mon golle moЖҙЖҙe; wano renndirgol e debbo mu'un fii Й“aЙ—tagol Alla jortoo jurriiya moЖҙЖҙo. Kuliree Alla ГұemtiЕӢgol Yamirooje Makko woЙ—Й—itoo haЙ—aaЙ—i Makko, wano ko O Shari'nani on e rwЙ“e mo'on. Nganndon wonde on kawroyay e Makko Гұalnde darngal, O YoЙ“ita on golle mo'on. Wewlin muumini en, an Annabiijo, neemaaji mawЙ“e tuma Й“e kawrata e Joomi maЙ“Й“e, Й“e tina Yeeso Makko Teddungo."
  2,224,"Wata on waЙ—u ngoondooje mon Й—en hujja heedorЙ—o golle Й—iggere e kulol Alla e moЖҙЖҙingol hakkunde yimЙ“e Й“en. Ko woni tun, si on woondii fii woppugol teertoo Й—iggere, on waЙ—ay tan kaffaara woondoore nden, jokkiton Й—iggere. Allah ko Nanoowo haalaaji mo'on, AnnduЙ—o golleeji mo'on; O YoЙ“itoyay on Й—um."